Jeremiah Moss, who writes a blog called Jeremiah's Vanishing New York (subtitled "The Book of Lamentations: A Bitterly Nostalgic View of the City in the Process of Extinction"), posted part of the story about Extra Place from The Talk About the City column, which appeared in The New Yorker newspaper in 1952.
