Set in an environment he doesn't yet know, he tells of events unknown to him, yet Mario Vargas Llosa intends to successfully implement his new project - he is currently working on a novel whose main character is Roger Casemant, an Irish nationalist who lived in the Congo for 20 years and traveled in the Amazon.
